item.description: Useless Machine was a mobile sandbox game (Unpiblished) MTRandom an alternative Random library for Unity3d designed to generate uniform Pseudo-Random deviates flowFit a Bioconductor package to estimate proliferation in cell-tracking dye studies FancyGene was a tool to generate PDF and PNG images of genes/domains and include them in presentations and papers Splicy aka Gene Chip splice machine, was a tool to store and display original data relatives to single probes mapping over Exons.
